data.text: Adult 40th Birthday Beer Gift Set INCLUDES 6 beer bottle sticker labels & 6 bottle neck labels in the gold 40th birthday theme, as well as 1 six-pack carrier with 4 black and gold birthday party stickers for decoration. 40th Birthday Party Beer bottle stickers each SIZE 3.5" wide x 3" tall, perfect for standard beer bottles or similarly sized soda bottles; Beer collar neck labels measure 3.5" long x 1.5" wide at the center. Beer bottle labels are quick to apply and will give your birthday gift a personal touch! HIGH QUALITY BIRTHDAY PARTY SUPPLIES: Adult 40th Birthday beer bottle labels are professionally printed on a sticker paper with a glossy coating. They are waterproof and can be used on bottles that will be chilled, just apply prior to chilling. Use the beer kit as the perfect birthday party gift or at a birthday party beverage bar for an impressive, coordinated display. EASY TO USE: Prepare your beverage bottles by ensuring they are room temperature. Removing the original bottle label is not necessary but is preferred. Carefully peel one “Cheers to 40 Years” sticker label from the backing and adhere to a bottle, starting at the edge and rolling to the opposite edge. Add the bottle neck label and place the completed bottle into the kraft paper carrier. Complete the party beer gift kit by adding the remaining 4 stickers to the sides of the six-pack carrier. MADE IN THE USA: Adult 40th Birthday - Gold - Birthday Party Beer Bottle Labels and Carrier is designed and manufactured at our Wisconsin facility using materials that are Made in the USA. Please Note: Beer in image is not included. Beer Bottle Labels No-Mess Glitter Print: Our beverage labels are designed with a printed image of glitter, eliminating glitter flake while maximizing bling effect!
